title: FS T205 Rube Marquard AUTO - BEST of 3 examples
author: hcv123

posts.post_title: FS T205 Rube Marquard AUTO - BEST of 3 examples
posts.post_content: Really special card right here.  It is 1 of 3 examples slabbed by PSA and by far the nicest of the 3.  Happy to provide images of the other 2 which can be found on VCP.  Probably worth getting this dual graded (if that's your thing).  Anyway.  $1799 net to me gets this insured and delivered to you (deliveries to New York add 8.625% sales tax).
